snippet.title: Tanki X – Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Tanki X is a multiplayer, tank-action game that’s out to prove that when it comes to tanks, there’s more than just thick shells and firepower…  

Sign up for a free account at http://tankix.com/en/

The trailer is made by Okta Studio - http://www.okta-studio.com
